<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; line-height:1.3em; vertical-align:middle;">
<div style="padding-top:0.25em; text-align:left; font-style:90%;"><b>Notes</b><br />
He is the father of <a href="/wiki/Erwin_Planck" title="Erwin Planck">Erwin Planck</a> who was hanged in 1945 by the <a href="/wiki/Gestapo" title="Gestapo">Gestapo</a> for his part in the <a href="/wiki/July_20_plot" title="July 20 plot" class="mw-redirect">July 20 plot</a>.</div>
</td>
</tr>
